to crush European wisdom,

00:02:57.190 --> 00:03:00.130 align:middle line:84%
because it was so
refined, so cultivated.

00:03:00.130 --> 00:03:02.180 align:middle line:84%
Which sounds funny
to say that today,

00:03:02.180 --> 00:03:04.420 align:middle line:84%
because we often associate
that with the East, which,

00:03:04.420 --> 00:03:08.230 align:middle line:84%
