anthroposophy, or theosophy,

00:03:40.390 --> 00:03:42.070 align:middle line:84%
or whatever-- lots
of different schools

00:03:42.070 --> 00:03:45.210 align:middle line:84%
and literally
hundreds of subgroups.

00:03:45.210 --> 00:03:47.180 align:middle line:84%
