served two purposes.

00:03:47.180 --> 00:03:49.340 align:middle line:84%
One was to prove the
student's devotion.

00:03:49.340 --> 00:03:50.140 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yes.

00:03:50.140 --> 00:03:53.500 align:middle line:84%
>> KRAMER: And to demonstrate
worthiness for real

00:03:53.500 --> 00:03:57.765 align:middle line:84%
world-shaping power to
alchemically change reality.

00:03:57.765 --> 00:03:59.140 align:middle line:84%
And the second
one, as I say, was

00:03:59.140 --> 00:04:03.670 align:middle line:84%
to protect the group from
execution, which was obviously

00:04:03.670 --> 00:04:05.600 align:middle line:90%
the worst case scenario.

00:04:05.600 --> 00:04:07.780 align:middle line:90%
But also exile.

00:04:07.780 --> 00:04:11.860 align:middle line:84%
So it would be quite common to
take a small religious group

00:04:11.860 --> 00:04:15.370 align:middle line:84%
from many counties in
England and exile them.

00:04:15.370 --> 00:04:17.079 align:middle line:84%
And say, we won't kill
you, because we're

00:04:17.079 --> 00:04:19.700 align:middle line:84%
very civilized people,
but you must leave.

00:04:19.700 --> 00:04:22.920 align:middle line:84%
And if you ever preach,
if you ever speak,

00:04:22.920 --> 00:04:25.060 align:middle line:84%
or if we ever catch
you practicing

00:04:25.060 --> 00:04:29.590 align:middle line:84%
this independent spirituality,
then we will prosecute,

00:04:29.590 --> 00:04:31.760 align:middle line:90%
which will lead to death.

00:04:31.760 --> 00:04:34.920 align:middle line:84%
So that was originally
why that came about.

00:04:34.920 --> 00:04:37.360 align:middle line:84%
And there's just
such a fear pattern

00:04:37.360 --> 00:04:41.410 align:middle line:84%
that that's been carried right
through the centuries really.

00:04:41.410 --> 00:04:45.430 align:middle line:84%
And as I was saying to you
earlier this afternoon,

00:04:45.430 --> 00:04:49.180 align:middle line:84%
there's a great American scholar
and mystical practitioner

00:04:49.180 --> 00:04:51.154 align:middle line:90%
called Paul Foster Case.

00:04:51.154 --> 00:04:52.570 align:middle line:84%
