the first people

00:04:52.570 --> 00:04:56.500 align:middle line:84%
who released these terrible
earth-shattering secrets

00:04:56.500 --> 00:05:02.660 align:middle line:84%
in a correspondence course in
the late 1800s, early 1900s.

00:05:02.660 --> 00:05:06.850 align:middle line:84%
