you know what, I'm

00:05:10.750 --> 00:05:15.040 align:middle line:84%
going to release this stuff
in a principled, rational,

00:05:15.040 --> 00:05:17.890 align:middle line:84%
sensitive, responsible
way-- in my way.

00:05:17.890 --> 00:05:19.870 align:middle line:84%
