those wisdom seeds

00:05:19.870 --> 00:05:22.640 align:middle line:90%
with everyone I see fit to.

00:05:22.640 --> 00:05:23.920 align:middle line:90%
And he did.

00:05:23.920 --> 00:05:27.170 align:middle line:84%
And most of the seeds,
people didn't recognize them.

00:05:27.170 --> 00:05:28.920 align:middle line:84%
Most of them, no one
knew what that meant.

00:05:28.920 --> 00:05:29.200 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Absolutely.

00:05:29.200 --> 00:05:29.340 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:05:29.340 --> 00:05:31.714 align:middle line:84%
>> KRAMER: Most people just
thought that's too difficult,

00:05:31.714 --> 00:05:32.560 align:middle line:90%
that's too hard.

00:05:32.560 --> 00:05:33.559 align:middle line:90%
I don't want to do that.

00:05:33.559 --> 00:05:35.190 align:middle line:90%
So they went away.

00:05:35.190 --> 00:05:39.510 align:middle line:84%
