serious spiritual humans

00:05:39.510 --> 00:05:42.870 align:middle line:84%
who wanted to better themselves
and to become something

00:05:42.870 --> 00:05:46.440 align:middle line:84%
more than just a comfortable
man, a comfortable woman.

00:05:46.440 --> 00:05:49.260 align:middle line:84%
They wanted to have an
ascendancy about them.

00:05:49.260 --> 00:05:51.770 align:middle line:84%
Took those seeds and
began to take them home,

00:05:51.770 --> 00:05:54.240 align:middle line:84%
