hermetic order-- just one,

00:06:04.320 --> 00:06:06.250 align:middle line:90%
but a very prominent one--

00:06:06.250 --> 00:06:09.720 align:middle line:84%
were actually privately
pleased with what Case did--

00:06:09.720 --> 00:06:11.280 align:middle line:90%
Paul Foster Case.

00:06:11.280 --> 00:06:15.720 align:middle line:84%
And his dissemination
responsibly-- mind--

00:06:15.720 --> 00:06:18.530 align:middle line:90%
of this great knowledge.

00:06:18.530 --> 00:06:21.750 align:middle line:84%
So although they were
publicly embarrassed by it,

00:06:21.750 --> 00:06:23.507 align:middle line:90%
privately with the bloody--

00:06:23.507 --> 00:06:25.090 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: They knew
