00:06:46.500 --> 00:06:48.530 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: So it's
self-selecting--

00:06:48.530 --> 00:06:49.075 align:middle line:90%
>> KRAMER: It's self-selecting.

00:06:49.075 --> 00:06:49.480 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: --because of that.

00:06:49.480 --> 00:06:50.520 align:middle line:84%
>> KRAMER: That's a
nice way of saying it.

00:06:50.520 --> 00:06:51.320 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:06:51.320 --> 00:06:52.320 align:middle line:90%
It totally is.

00:06:52.320 --> 00:06:54.960 align:middle line:84%
And I would say,
the difference today

00:06:54.960 --> 00:06:59.130 align:middle line:84%
