00:07:30.910 --> 00:07:33.700 align:middle line:84%
It's unlikely anyone
is going to execute you

00:07:33.700 --> 00:07:35.120 align:middle line:90%
for what you believe.

00:07:35.120 --> 00:07:37.220 align:middle line:84%
So initiation is
self-initiation now.

00:07:37.220 --> 00:07:38.020 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yes.

00:07:38.020 --> 00:07:38.920 align:middle line:90%
>> KRAMER: That's the big shift.

00:07:38.920 --> 00:07:39.720 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: It is.

00:07:39.720 --> 00:07:43.480 align:middle line:84%
