00:08:14.080 --> 00:08:14.880 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Exactly.

00:08:14.880 --> 00:08:17.470 align:middle line:84%
>> KRAMER: So only
through typically 1, 2, 3,

00:08:17.470 --> 00:08:22.550 align:middle line:84%
