what resources do

00:38:56.660 --> 00:38:57.950 align:middle line:90%
you want to generate for what?

00:38:57.950 --> 00:38:58.490 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: For what purpose?

00:38:58.490 --> 00:38:59.830 align:middle line:84%
>> KRAMER: Fantastic,
juicy experiment.

00:38:59.830 --> 00:39:00.570 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Exactly.

00:39:00.570 --> 00:39:02.611 align:middle line:84%
>> KRAMER: And if you want
