beautiful thing,

00:39:11.135 --> 00:39:12.260 align:middle line:90%
you don't need any of that.

00:39:12.260 --> 00:39:12.620 align:middle line:90%
Great.

00:39:12.620 --> 00:39:13.830 align:middle line:90%
That's fine as well.

00:39:13.830 --> 00:39:17.280 align:middle line:84%
So wealth is like absolutely
nothing to do with it.

00:39:17.280 --> 00:39:19.982 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: And also
looking at the other side,

00:39:19.982 --> 00:39:22.190 align:middle line:84%
people have taken it to the
extreme when they're very

00:39:22.190 --> 00:39:24.500 align:middle line:84%
frustrated about their
