of integrity and wisdom?

00:41:47.820 --> 00:41:52.300 align:middle line:84%
And go to any G20, G7,
G8, whatever the heck--

00:41:52.300 --> 00:41:53.830 align:middle line:84%
go to any of those
giant summits,

00:41:53.830 --> 00:41:56.770 align:middle line:84%
look at all the world leaders
