wisdom and integrity?

00:41:59.125 --> 00:42:01.000 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: I don't think
we have to go there.

00:42:01.000 --> 00:42:01.880 align:middle line:84%
>> KRAMER: It's a
simple one, isn't it?

00:42:01.880 --> 00:42:02.110 align:middle line:90%
Simple.

00:42:02.110 --> 00:42:02.560 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Yeah, it's simple.

00:42:02.560 --> 00:42:03.560 align:middle line:84%
>> KRAMER: The answer
is no, they're not.

00:42:03.560 --> 00:42:04.360 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Of course, not.

00:42:04.360 --> 00:42:06.610 align:middle line:84%
>> KRAMER: And when you
go to the giant technology

00:42:06.610 --> 00:42:07.567 align:middle line:90%
