it, but the people who run it,

00:42:25.200 --> 00:42:27.280 align:middle line:84%
the people who
determine policy--

00:42:27.280 --> 00:42:29.250 align:middle line:84%
are they full of
wisdom and integrity?

00:42:29.250 --> 00:42:32.230 align:middle line:90%
Do they embody and exude that?

