that is through shadow.

00:55:01.430 --> 00:55:04.250 align:middle line:84%
So to remove your
emotional import

00:55:04.250 --> 00:55:07.190 align:middle line:90%
you have to meet despair.

00:55:07.190 --> 00:55:10.820 align:middle line:84%
Total despair, where you're
at the edge, and over the edge

00:55:10.820 --> 00:55:11.630 align:middle line:90%
is nothingness.

00:55:11.630 --> 00:55:12.430 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: I agree.

00:55:12.430 --> 00:55:15.110 align:middle line:84%
>> KRAMER: At that
point, now you begin.

00:55:15.110 --> 00:55:16.730 align:middle line:90%
You draw the fool card.

00:55:16.730 --> 00:55:19.067 align:middle line:84%
Everything you thought
was right was wrong.

00:55:19.067 --> 00:55:20.900 align:middle line:84%
Everything you thought
was wrong, was right.

00:55:20.900 --> 00:55:22.880 align:middle line:84%
Everything is upside
down and back to front.

00:55:22.880 --> 00:55:24.500 align:middle line:90%
You start from scratch.

00:55:24.500 --> 00:55:26.570 align:middle line:90%
Everything is reduced to ashes.

00:55:26.570 --> 00:55:30.720 align:middle line:84%
At that point, you then say,
OK, all my foundations are gone.

00:55:30.720 --> 00:55:31.520 align:middle line:90%
I have nothing.

00:55:31.520 --> 00:55:32.436 align:middle line:90%
I'm not sure who I am.

00:55:32.436 --> 00:55:33.590 align:middle line:90%
I'm not sure what-- good.

00:55:33.590 --> 00:55:34.020 align:middle line:90%
Good.

00:55:34.020 --> 00:55:34.450 align:middle line:90%
Good.

00:55:34.450 --> 00:55:35.330 align:middle line:90%
Good.

00:55:35.330 --> 00:55:37.430 align:middle line:90%
Identity must be the Phoenix.

00:55:37.430 --> 00:55:41.280 align:middle line:84%
The first emblem of the United
States seal was not an eagle,

00:55:41.280 --> 00:55:42.460 align:middle line:90%
it was a Phoenix.

00:55:42.460 --> 00:55:44.430 align:middle line:90%
And it was reduced to ashes.

00:55:44.430 --> 00:55:47.960 align:middle line:84%
And that Phoenix, what
comes from those ashes is

00:55:47.960 --> 00:55:50.360 align:middle line:90%
made of fire, is made of light.

00:55:50.360 --> 00:55:53.960 align:middle line:84%
And that light is
inherently sovereign.

00:55:53.960 --> 00:55:58.480 align:middle line:84%
That is the thing that emanates
us, that emanates into us.

00:55:58.480 --> 00:56:03.410 align:middle line:84%
That is automatically free,
automatically has liberty,

00:56:03.410 --> 00:56:05.540 align:middle line:90%
automatically self-determining.

00:56:05.540 --> 00:56:08.480 align:middle line:84%
So to dissolve that
despair, you have

00:56:08.480 --> 00:56:10.190 align:middle line:90%
to embrace your own journey.

00:56:10.190 --> 00:56:15.140 align:middle line:84%
Do not affiliate with
Empire menu organizations.

00:56:15.140 --> 00:56:17.899 align:middle line:84%
Practically any major organ--
just forget all of that.

00:56:17.899 --> 00:56:19.190 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Forget institutions.

00:56:19.190 --> 00:56:20.648 align:middle line:84%
>> KRAMER: Forget
the institutions.

00:56:20.648 --> 00:56:22.220 align:middle line:90%
They're not here to help you.

00:56:22.220 --> 00:56:25.460 align:middle line:84%
And for some people, who've
really put into that,

00:56:25.460 --> 00:56:27.440 align:middle line:84%
and been out there
on the streets,

00:56:27.440 --> 00:56:30.280 align:middle line:84%
and been flesh and blood
involved, that's a tough one.

00:56:30.280 --> 00:56:31.700 align:middle line:90%
That's a really tough one.

00:56:31.700 --> 00:56:34.880 align:middle line:84%
But I think when you search
deep inside and you see,

00:56:34.880 --> 00:56:36.230 align:middle line:90%
you realize you've been had.

00:56:36.230 --> 00:56:39.200 align:middle line:84%
And that's a tough one there
to know you've been conned.

00:56:39.200 --> 00:56:40.850 align:middle line:90%
There's been a long con.

00:56:40.850 --> 00:56:41.750 align:middle line:90%
Maybe 50 years.

00:56:41.750 --> 00:56:42.650 align:middle line:90%
Maybe 80 years.

00:56:42.650 --> 00:56:45.210 align:middle line:90%
A long con in your life.

00:56:45.210 --> 00:56:49.220 align:middle line:84%
You have to have the
humility, the humble truth

00:56:49.220 --> 00:56:52.850 align:middle line:84%
within yourself to say, I
may have been conned here.

00:56:52.850 --> 00:56:53.900 align:middle line:90%
Let's do an experiment.

00:56:53.900 --> 00:56:57.410 align:middle line:84%
Let's start again from scratch
and build new foundations.

00:56:57.410 --> 00:56:58.970 align:middle line:90%
What is medicine?

00:56:58.970 --> 00:57:00.500 align:middle line:90%
What is food?

00:57:00.500 --> 00:57:02.000 align:middle line:90%
What is leadership?

00:57:02.000 --> 00:57:04.730 align:middle line:90%
How do we educate each other?

00:57:04.730 --> 00:57:06.070 align:middle line:90%
What is this for?

00:57:06.070 --> 00:57:06.870 align:middle line:90%
What is this?

00:57:06.870 --> 00:57:08.840 align:middle line:84%
Don't allow anyone
else to tell you.

00:57:08.840 --> 00:57:10.550 align:middle line:90%
Build those foundations.

00:57:10.550 --> 00:57:13.640 align:middle line:84%
Make sure in your life
you have wise elders.

00:57:13.640 --> 00:57:18.480 align:middle line:84%
People who have been on the
path for decades, sovereign,

00:57:18.480 --> 00:57:22.530 align:middle line:84%
independent, who you can speak
to, who embody the teaching,

00:57:22.530 --> 00:57:24.177 align:middle line:90%
not just talk about it.

00:57:24.177 --> 00:57:26.510 align:middle line:84%
Like I can just say this and
then go over there and just

00:57:26.510 --> 00:57:29.530 align:middle line:90%
be a fool.

00:57:29.530 --> 00:57:33.920 align:middle line:84%
But, you know, this woman,
this man, always embody it.

00:57:33.920 --> 00:57:36.740 align:middle line:84%
This is a teacher, because they
walk it when no one's looking.

00:57:36.740 --> 00:57:38.169 align:middle line:90%
This is what they do.

00:57:38.169 --> 00:57:39.710 align:middle line:84%
Have those people
in your life and it

00:57:39.710 --> 00:57:41.670 align:middle line:90%
will accelerate that process.

00:57:41.670 --> 00:57:44.600 align:middle line:84%
There's no need to take another
50 years to get to truth.

00:57:44.600 --> 00:57:49.250 align:middle line:84%
So what we're talking about is
one's preparedness for honesty.

00:57:49.250 --> 00:57:52.280 align:middle line:84%
Which I would say, in my
teaching-- we have many maxims,

00:57:52.280 --> 00:57:53.390 align:middle line:90%
many axioms--

00:57:53.390 --> 00:57:57.050 align:middle line:84%
one is how truthful
can you afford to be?

00:57:57.050 --> 00:57:57.994 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Exactly.

00:57:57.994 --> 00:57:59.660 align:middle line:84%
And this takes us
right back full circle

00:57:59.660 --> 00:58:01.220 align:middle line:84%
to the beginning of
the conversation,

00:58:01.220 --> 00:58:04.160 align:middle line:84%
because these esoteric
paths of knowledge

00:58:04.160 --> 00:58:07.090 align:middle line:84%
require the same
open-mindedness and humility.

00:58:07.090 --> 00:58:10.130 align:middle line:84%
This going in, not
assuming you know anything,

00:58:10.130 --> 00:58:11.450 align:middle line:90%
and starting from scratch.

00:58:11.450 --> 00:58:14.289 align:middle line:84%
And letting it be revealed
to you through your own self.

00:58:14.289 --> 00:58:16.580 align:middle line:84%
>> KRAMER: You have to be
prepared to destroy yourself.

00:58:16.580 --> 00:58:19.490 align:middle line:84%
To reduce yourself to
ashes and know that nothing

00:58:19.490 --> 00:58:22.400 align:middle line:84%
can be destroyed
in its divine form.

00:58:22.400 --> 00:58:24.230 align:middle line:90%
The self disappears.

00:58:24.230 --> 00:58:26.970 align:middle line:84%
Put yourself on the
floor, fetal position,

00:58:26.970 --> 00:58:28.520 align:middle line:90%
work your way back up.

00:58:28.520 --> 00:58:32.280 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: The stronger the
ego position, the harder it is.

00:58:32.280 --> 00:58:33.080 align:middle line:90%
>> KRAMER: Sure.

00:58:33.080 --> 00:58:35.413 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: So that's always
the challenge with humanity.

00:58:35.413 --> 00:58:36.260 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

00:58:36.260 --> 00:58:38.400 align:middle line:90%
We are just about out of time.

00:58:38.400 --> 00:58:39.200 align:middle line:90%
Any final thoughts?

00:58:39.200 --> 00:58:40.440 align:middle line:90%
That was so beautiful.

00:58:40.440 --> 00:58:41.240 align:middle line:90%
>> KRAMER: No.

00:58:41.240 --> 00:58:43.640 align:middle line:10%
I would just encourage
people that if you ever

00:58:43.640 --> 00:58:48.590 align:middle line:10%
feel that there's the system
that is against humankind,

00:58:48.590 --> 00:58:49.622 align:middle line:10%
don't politicize it.

00:58:49.622 --> 00:58:51.080 align:middle line:10%
It's nothing to do
with what we see

00:58:51.080 --> 00:58:53.120 align:middle line:10%
on television and the internet.

00:58:53.120 --> 00:58:57.840 align:middle line:84%
If you self-determine in every
area of life-- emotionally,

00:58:57.840 --> 00:59:00.300 align:middle line:84%
spiritually,
sexually, physically,

00:59:00.300 --> 00:59:02.690 align:middle line:84%
artistically-- when
you self-determine,

00:59:02.690 --> 00:59:04.640 align:middle line:90%
you dissolve the Empire.

00:59:04.640 --> 00:59:08.240 align:middle line:84%
So don't ever believe
anything outside of yourself.

00:59:08.240 --> 00:59:10.700 align:middle line:84%
Self-determine and
trust the wise elders

00:59:10.700 --> 00:59:14.540 align:middle line:84%
who embody in your life
and all will be well.

00:59:14.540 --> 00:59:15.870 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Hear, hear.

